  <div class="container" style="max-width:840px;text-align:center">
    <p style="font-size:1.02rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7">Once your kit is sorted, see what fuels the climb on our <a href="/food-on-the-mountain" style="color:var(--amber-cta);font-weight:600">food and altitude menu</a> guide, and how we keep camp clean and climbers healthy in the <a href="/hygiene" style="color:var(--amber-cta);font-weight:600">hygiene and cleanliness</a> guide.</p>
  </div>
